    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your heart’s desire is with man to mingle as one,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To dwell with man, an eternal bond to form,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Twas for this dream You became man, uplifting man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That God and man, heaven and earth, be joined for aye,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s house, heav’n’s gate, now descends, Your dream to attain."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From heav’n You came as my bread of eternal life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By eating You, I can now enjoy Your life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Brought to His house, the Father’s love for You is mine,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’m joined, a branch, to You, the vine—union divine,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By bearing fruit, this relationship multiplies."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Abide in love, so His life in us may flow free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By mutual love, His disciples we will be;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The more we’re joined, the more we’re built organically,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And by His word we’re sanctified, not of the world,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As one new man, corporate God-man living we’ll see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord, I place myself on the altar for You,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For Your desire, that Your dream may become true."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As for my life, I’d gladly dwell in a lowly tent,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be a drink off’ring outpoured for man"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s pillar, stand to fulfill God’s eternal plan."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
